Recommended deck flow:
1) Title + team
2) Client context + problem statement
3) Dataset overview + key challenges
4) ETL pipeline (before/after quality metrics)
5) KPI framework (definitions + why these KPIs)
6) EDA highlights (35 key findings)
7) Statistical analysis (evidence for decisions)
8) Tableau dashboards (exec + ops, how to use)
9) Recommendations (prioritized, measurable)
10) Impact estimation + next steps

